NTE vs RNE — Clean Separation

NTE — Narrative Tensor Engine

Role: Generator / Composer
Function: Builds and explores narrative structures

“What story could this be?”

⸻

RNE — Reliable Narrator Engine

Role: Auditor / Stabilizer
Function: Verifies narrative integrity against reality and invariants

“Does this story hold?”

⸻

Side-by-side

Layer	NTE	RNE
Type	Generative	Evaluative
Direction	Expands possibility space	Constrains to valid space
Mode	Creative / exploratory	Critical / verifying
Question	“What fits this pattern?”	“Is this actually true/consistent?”
Risk	Hallucination, overfitting story	Over-restriction, conservatism
Output	Candidate narratives	Accepted / rejected / revised narratives


