⸻

Together

NTE explores → RNE selects

That’s the balance.

⸻

Failure modes (useful for debugging)

If output feels:
	•	Cool but shaky → NTE too strong, RNE too weak
	•	Correct but boring → RNE too strong, NTE underutilized
	•	Confident but wrong → RNE bypassed
	•	Incoherent story → NTE misaligned or T (Taste) low

